# CSS Variables & Design System

## CRITICAL: Use CSS Variables for All Values

**NEVER use hardcoded pixel values.** Your project has a comprehensive design system in `styles/variables.css` with predefined spacing, sizing, and color values.

## Global Variables

- ALL CSS variables are defined in `styles/variables.css`
- **NEVER define new root-level variables - use existing ones or calc()**
- Define at `:root` level only

## Your Project's CSS Variables

